15 BE IT ENACTED BY THE PEOPLE OF THE STATE OF OKLAHOMA:
16 SECTION 1. AMENDATORY 59 O.S. 2021, Section 15.8, as
17 last amended by Section 1, Chapter 25, O.S.L. 2023 (59 O.S. Supp.
18 2024, Section 15.8), is amended to read as follows:
19 Section 15.8. A. A qualification applicant to qualify as a
20 candidate for examination shall file an application for
21 qualification in a format approved by the Oklahoma Accountancy
22 Board. The fee for the qualification application shall be
23 determined by the Board and shall not exceed Three Hundred Dollars
24 ($300.00). Every qualification applicant to qualify as a candidate
